=2E (The last time Trump was president,=
 the U.S.D.A. ended up spending billio=
ns of extra dollars to bail out farmers who were impacted by Trump=E2=80=99=
s trade wars.)

Other players could include U.S. Secretary of Agriculture-designee Brooke R=
ollins and even R.F.K. Jr., who, some Farm Bill advocates fear, might meddl=
e with the food supply if confirmed as H.H.S secretary, under the
auspices of =E2=80=9CMaking American Healthy Again.=E2=80=9D On the legisla=
tive side, the Stabenow retirement means that Amy Klobuchar is a frontrunne=
