ior to be considered for ranking membership of <i>any</i> committee, let al=
one Ag, let alone amid negotiations over the Farm Bill=E2=80=94the last ver=
sion of which passed a month before she was first sworn into the House. She=
 was also one of the first House Democrats to publicly call on Biden to end=
 his reelection campaign, last summer, and helped keep the =E2=80=9CDump Bi=
den=E2=80=9D movement from losing momentum over the Fourth of July weekend.=
<br/><br/>In my conversations with a half-dozen or so House Democratic sour=
ces, I heard respect for Craig=E2=80=99s willingness to stick her neck out=
=E2=80=94often alone=E2=80=94on these issues. The reason such a
junior member is in contention for this slot is because, besides Costa, oth=
er Democrats passed up the opportunity to challenge Scott. She=E2=80=99s al=
